<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.6.5">
<l>kavvaik kaḷiṟṟu maṉṉar māḷak kalimāṉtēr</l>
<l>aivark kāyaṉ ṟamari luyttā ṉūrpōlum</l>
<l>maivait tilaṅku kaṇṇār taṅkaḷ moḻiyoppāṉ</l>
<l>kovvaik kaṉivāyk kiḷḷai pēcuṅ kuṟuṅkuṭiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Kuṟuṅkuṭi, where parakeets with kovvai fruit[-hued] beaks say [words]</l>
<l>To resemble the speech of those whose eyes glimmer, having put on kohl,</l>
<l>Is like the city of the one who drove the chariot with lively horses long ago</l>
<l>On the battlefield for the Five</l>
<l rend="indent">so that kings with trumpeting elephants perished.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
